<h1>Rubixir</h1>
<div>
  Rubixir is a Rubik's Cube sandbox, made for the <a href="https://www.42.fr/" target="_blank">42 programming school</a> project Rubik. The languages used are:<br>

  <ul>
  <li>plain Elixir for the main logic, in a standalone module that provides an API to manipulate and solve a Rubik's Cube</li> 
  <li>the Elixir <a href="https://www.phoenixframework.org/" target="_blank">Phoenix web framework</a> for this webpage</li> 
  <li>JavaScript and <a href="https://threejs.org/" target="_blank">three.js</a> for the 3D visualization</li> 
  </ul>

